title: copy second profile data from pixel 3a to 4a5g
content:
I have setup my pixel 4a5g on the main profile but have struggled to copy my second profile data.
I have added the second profile and its gmail account but do not have the cable transfer option I had for the first profile. 
Is this possible?
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4a (5G)
